<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/595040066/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Progressive and global assessment will be based on the work done in class during the team sessions, the initial and final project presentations and the initial and final project reports.

In case there is a need for a referred examination, a written exam on machine learning and neural network fundamentals will be conducted and the final project will be reassessed. The project reassessment will be compulsory for those students who get a grade less than five points (5.0) in the progressive assessment. For the rest of students, this activity will be optional."""@es ;
